达 30 年而广为人知。 公司在声明中提及，山崎和佳奈此前已因病疗养，但「药石无效」，于 4 月 18 日离世。遵照家属意愿，葬礼已由近亲私下举行。 消息确认后，Twitter 、 Reddit 等平台充满了动漫迷和游戏玩家的哀思。网友们纷纷回忆她塑造的角色，尤其是感谢她为毛利兰注入的灵魂，并感叹世界又失去了一位伟大的声优。她所配角色还有《橘子酱男孩》秋月茗子、《GS 美神极乐大作战》玛丽亚、《格斗美神武龙》毛兰、《海贼王》诺琪高、娜美及斯卡莱特以及《十二国记》恭王珠晶等。 小兰姐姐再见！《柯南》毛利兰声优去世 享年 61 岁"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "91 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2038599075206000974"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIseCtlrjEqdUKEAMaCTExOTUxNjc4OSC2xprQBjAAOCFADXITMjAzODU5OTA3NTIwNjAwMDk3NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1778854078.181098", "card_id": "Q_2038396347775022033", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 33}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美以袭击伊朗进入第 77 天，当前局势如何？哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-2216305bfe897ca7601c1bb99aad6025_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "90 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2038396347775022033"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIseCtlrjEqdUKEAMaCTExOTUxMDI2OSDozJfQBjAAODdADnITMjAzODM5NjM0Nzc3NTAyMjAzM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1778854078.181700", "card_id": "Q_2038577207740715513", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "外交部介绍美国总统特朗普访华情况，称「两国元首达成一系列新共识」，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据外交部网站消息，外交部发言人就美国总统特朗普访华情况答记者问。 问：5 月 14 日，习近平主席为正在访华的美国总统特朗普举行系列国事活动，国内外高度关注。中方能否进一步介绍相关情况？ 答：应习近平主席邀请，美国总统特朗普正在对中国进行国事访问。这是中美两国元首继去年 10 月釜山之后再次面对面会晤，也是美国总统时隔 9 年再次访华。5 月 14 日，习近平主席为特朗普总统举行欢迎仪式和欢迎宴会，同特朗普总统举行会谈，并共同参观天坛。两国元首就事关两国和世界的重大问题深入交换意见，达成一系列新共识。 两国元首赞同将构建「中美建设性战略稳定关系」作为中美关系新定位，为未来 3 年乃至更长时间的中美关系提供战略指引，推动两国关系稳定、健康、可持续发展，为世界带来更多和平、繁荣、进步。 两国元首还就妥善处理彼此关切达成重要共识，同意就国际地区问题加强沟通和协调。 两国元首互动促进了相互理解，加深了彼此信任，推进了务实合作，增进了两国人民的福祉，为世界注入了亟需的稳定性和确定性。外交部发言人就美国总统特朗普访华情况答记者问 - 中新网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-4c318c2ae65c0c6e28ba8407dd9057ec.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "89 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2038577207740715513"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIseCtlrjEqdUKEAMaCTExOTUxNDk2MSDZnZrQBjAAOCpAD3ITMjAzODU3NzIwNzc0MDcxNTUxM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1778854078.182856", "card_id": "Q_272169012", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 64}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "法国人的性格是怎样的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "留学生一般跟法国人打交道的多吗？还是在中国人的圈子里面自己玩？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-f9277e48858f8d37674b625a91be3755_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "88 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/272169012"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IseCtlrjEqdUKEAMaCDIyNzU2OTg1IMmVwdYFMAA4+AJAEHIJMjcyMTY5MDEyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1778854078.183297", "card_id": "Q_2038185898815251799", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 20}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "「九章四号」量子计算原型机研制成功，求解特定问题比最快超算快 10 的 54 次方倍，这意味着什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "目前世界上最快的超级计算机，求解特定数学问题约需 10 的 42 次方年。由中国科学家最新研制成功的「九章四号」量子计算原型机只需要 25 微秒，比超算快超过亿亿亿亿亿亿倍。 「九章四号」量子计算原型机局部。新华社发 中国科学技术大学潘建伟、陆朝阳、张强、刘乃乐等组成的研究团队联合国内多家科研单位，成功研制出 1024 个量子压缩态输入、 8176 模式的可编程量子计算原型机「九章四号」，首次操纵和探测高达 3050 个光子的量子态，再度刷新光量子信息技术世界纪录。国际知名学术期刊《自然》13 日发表了该成果。 什么是量子计算机？它和我们日常用的电脑有什么区别？「九章四号」为何那么强？这次成果意味着啥？新华社记者独家采访科研团队，带来权威解读。 "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-4b47bf52ef879688cc24c6dfcd66d126_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "87 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2038185898815251799"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIseCtlrjEqdUKEAMaCTExOTQ5OTkzOCDpxJTQBjAAOEZAEXITMjAzODE4NTg5ODgxNTI1MTc5OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1778854078.183980", "card_id": "Q_2006125343182963479", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2026 年像 4B 、 7B 、 13B 这种大模型到底有什么使用场景？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "87 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2006125343182963479"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIseCtlrjEqdUKEAMaCTExODQzNTA5NCCx/8HMBjAAOGRAEnITMjAwNjEyNTM0MzE4Mjk2MzQ3OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1778854078.184256", "card_id": "Q_530331449", "feed_specific": {"